# AI Boundary Rules

AI is an enhancement layer, not the source of truth.

Allowed AI responsibilities:
- photo condition summary
- visible issue detection
- recommended works
- redesign concept text
- report wording
- future OpenAI Vision wrappers

Not allowed:
- pricing calculations
- ROI calculations
- VAT calculations
- profit calculations
- legal or structural certainty

Mock AI outputs must be clearly structured so real OpenAI integration can replace them later.

Keep AI outputs separate from deterministic engines.
